Package: functionsframework
Title: Functions Framework
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Averi",
           family = "Kitsch",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "akitsch@google.com")
Description: FaaS (Function as a service) framework for writing portable R
  functions. The functions framework configures an entry point that starts R
  server that runs user's code on HTTP request.
Depends:
  R (>= 3.1.0),
  plumber (>= 0.4.6),
  optparse (>= 1.6.4)
